<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA44">
<l>vakaicērnta naṉṉeñcu nāvuṭaiya vāyu</l>
<l>mikavāyntu vīḻā veṉilu mikavāyntu</l>
<l>mālaittām vāḻttā tiruppa rituvaṉṟē</l>
<l>mēlaittāñ ceyyum viṉai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though one says the good heart and the mouth possessing a tongue</l>
<l>joined in [that] way very befittingly will not fall – this, isn’t it?,</l>
<l>for those who keep not praising Māl, very befittingly,</l>
<l>is the deed they do further.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
